{
 "rules": [
  {
   "id": "intro-dismiss-q",
   "comment": "按 Q(切建造=任务第一步指示)即收起开场序章,自然衔接玩法。",
   "on": {
    "event": "input",
    "filter": {
     "action": "q",
     "phase": "pressed"
    }
   },
   "do": [
    {
     "set": "@intro_panel.Ui.ox",
     "to": -6000
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "intro-dismiss-built",
   "comment": "兜底:开始建造也收起序章。",
   "on": {
    "event": "built"
   },
   "do": [
    {
     "set": "@intro_panel.Ui.ox",
     "to": -6000
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "ending-show",
   "comment": "通关 settlement-thrived/game-won → 弹结局,收起其它 overlay。",
   "on": {
    "event": "game-won"
   },
   "do": [
    {
     "set": "@ending_panel.Ui.ox",
     "to": 0
    },
    {
     "set": "@intro_panel.Ui.ox",
     "to": -6000
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "beat-beacon",
   "comment": "剧情旁白:beacon",
   "on": {
    "event": "quest-done"
   },
   "if": [
    [
     "event.id",
     "==",
     "beacon"
    ]
   ],
   "do": [
    {
     "set": "@narration_lbl.UiLabel.content",
     "to": "信标转起来了,红灯一明一灭。没人应答——可这片黑里,总算有个亮着的东西。"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "beat-wheat",
   "comment": "剧情旁白:wheat",
   "on": {
    "event": "quest-done"
   },
   "if": [
    [
     "event.id",
     "==",
     "wheat"
    ]
   ],
   "do": [
    {
     "set": "@narration_lbl.UiLabel.content",
     "to": "头一把麦子,比想的瘦小。可这是赭土星头一样,肯为你长出来的东西。"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "beat-first-companion",
   "comment": "剧情旁白:first-companion",
   "on": {
    "event": "quest-done"
   },
   "if": [
    [
     "event.id",
     "==",
     "first-companion"
    ]
   ],
   "do": [
    {
     "set": "@narration_lbl.UiLabel.content",
     "to": "Lio 把行李往墙角一扔:「比我上个落脚点强。」有人能嫌弃你这个家,也算桩好事。"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "beat-立足",
   "comment": "剧情旁白:立足",
   "on": {
    "event": "quest-done"
   },
   "if": [
    [
     "event.id",
     "==",
     "立足"
    ]
   ],
   "do": [
    {
     "set": "@narration_lbl.UiLabel.content",
     "to": "三面墙立起来,风小了。算不上家,但夜里总算能合上眼。"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "beat-温饱",
   "comment": "剧情旁白:温饱",
   "on": {
    "event": "quest-done"
   },
   "if": [
    [
     "event.id",
     "==",
     "温饱"
    ]
   ],
   "do": [
    {
     "set": "@narration_lbl.UiLabel.content",
     "to": "粮仓头回有了吃不完的麦子。你留出一份没动——这点余裕,来得不容易。"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": "beat-成群",
   "comment": "剧情旁白:成群",
   "on": {
    "event": "quest-done"
   },
   "if": [
    [
     "event.id",
     "==",
     "成群"
    ]
   ],
   "do": [
    {
     "set": "@narration_lbl.UiLabel.content",
     "to": "人多起来了。有人替你看田,有人半夜还在敲敲打打。荒原没变,只是不再安静了。"
    }
   ]
  }
 ]
}